# City Library Digital Management System (Java)

## Project Description
This project is a Java console-based application developed for managing a digital library system.  
It helps to manage:
- Book records
- Member records
- Book issue and return system
- File storage for data persistence

This project uses:
- Java Collections Framework (List, Set, Map)
- File Handling
- Sorting using Comparable
- Searching feature

---

## Technologies Used
- Java (JDK 8+)
- File Handling (BufferedReader/Writer)
- Collection Framework

---

## Features
- Add and manage books
- Add members
- Issue and return books
- Search books by title/author/category
- Sort books by title
- Data saved in text files

